itemDescription: Bishop of Derby; Clerk of the Closet; Bishop of Dunwich (1940-2008)

wikipedia_page.main: Jonathan Sansbury Bailey,  (24 February 1940 – 9 December 2008) was an English Anglican bishop. He was Bishop of Dunwich from 1992 to 1995, Bishop of Derby from 1995 to 2005, and Clerk of the Closet from 1997 to 2005.
